        "heading" : "Design rules:",
        "line" : 107,
        "lines" : [
          "**Test first** — never fix without confirming broken",
          "**Re-test after fix** — verify the fix worked",
          "**Timeout everything** — `timeout N` on any command that could hang",
          "**Use helpers** — `pass()`, `fail()`, `fixed()`, `skip()`",
          "**Idempotent fixes** — safe to run repeatedly",
          "**Skip gracefully** — `skip()` when a prerequisite is missing, don't fail"
        ],
        "role" : "inert"
